<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Editor de Código - Bootcamp Portal</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <style>
    #editor-container { height: 500px; border-radius: 1rem; overflow: hidden; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1e2f 0%, #3a3a6a 100%);">
  <div class="main-card p-8 max-w-2xl w-full flex flex-col items-center gap-6" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.10); border-radius: 1.5rem; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.37); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);">
    <h1 class="text-2xl mb-1" style="font-weight:600; color:#fff; letter-spacing:0.01em;">Editor de Código</h1>
    <div class="subtitle text-center mb-4" style="color:#e0e0f0;">Aquí puedes escribir y probar código en línea.</div>
    <div id="editor-container" class="w-full bg-white">
      <!-- Editor embebido: StackBlitz, CodeMirror, Monaco, etc. -->
      <iframe src="https://stackblitz.com/edit/javascript-oqjv2y?embed=1&file=index.js" width="100%" height="500" frameborder="0" style="border-radius:1rem;"></iframe>
    </div>
    <a href="/dashboard" class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-300 hover:underline">Volver al dashboard</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
